			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "100% drop chance from a loot bag: The Sword of the Cosmos has inifinite amounts of damage. It also has two abilities. Right-Click will kill all the agressive mobs nearby. Shift Right-Clicking will kill all the mobs nearby. Oh, and of course. It can destroy Chaos Crystals with one hit. One of the quests which represent the END of The Decursio Project."
