		{
			x: 1.5d
			y: -4.0d
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "Might be able to mine Bedrock: The World Breaker can mine through almost anything with a very high level of the Fortune enchantment. The Pickaxe has a secondary mode which can be activated using Shift Righ-Click. In this mode, it will be able to mine very large areas of stone. All of the mined blocks, will be added to your inventory in the form of a Matter Cluster. All the items can be retrived by Right-Clicking the Cluster. Also, in this mode it will allow you to pick up Bedrock using Right-Click. One of the quests which represent the END of The Decursio Project."
			dependencies: [
