			x: -1.5d
			y: 1.0d
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "This will not save any forest: If you attempt to mine with it while holding the Shift key, you'll instantly chop down the entire tree. However, if you Shift Right-Click with the Axe in the air, all the trees in fron of you, will be instantly erased and they'll be added to your inventory in the form of a Matter Cluster. All the items can be retrived by Right-Clicking the Cluster. One of the quests which represent the END of The Decursio Project."
