		{
			x: 1.5d
			y: 1.0d
			shape: "diamond"
			subtitle: "Removing all the dirt in the world?: The Planet Eater, similar to the other tools, will have two operating modes. In the main one, you'll have a regular, very fast, shovel. However, in the secondary one (activated with Shift Right-Click), you'll have a massive excavator. It will harvest all the blocks in a huge area and it will add them to your inventory in the form of a Matter Cluster. The items can be retrived from the Cluster using Right-Click. One of the quests which represent the END of The Decursio Project."
